Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:08.78,Default,Oka,0,0,0,,{\blur0}Vậy bây giờ đi, được chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:10.28,Default,Ush,0,0,0,,{\blur0}Ừm!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:21.46,Default,Oka,0,0,0,,{\blur0}Mang đủ hết chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:22.17,Default,Ush,0,0,0,,{\blur0}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:24.13,Default,Oka,0,0,0,,{\blur0}Cửa nẻo khóa hết chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:25.05,Default,Ush,0,0,0,,{\blur0}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:26.97,Default,Oka,0,0,0,,{\blur0}Rồi, xuất phát!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:28.97,Default,Ush,0,0,0,,{\blur0}Ô!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:39.20,Default,Oka,0,0,0,,{\blur0\i1}Trước đây, mỗi khi gặp Ushio,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.31,0:21:41.34,Default,Oka,0,0,0,,{\blur0\i1}Sanae-san và ông già luôn có mặt.
